<MELItem itemNbr="28-22-06" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-28-22-06.1.2-28-22-06">
<Title>Fuel Balance Switch</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)" opsIndicator="(O)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Crossfeed valve is verified to operate normally before each departure.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Operations procedure is used for fuel balancing.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Verify crossfeed valve operates normally (AMM DDG 28-22-06). </Para>
<Para>(Required by AD 2019-19-10) </Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Gain access to the crossfeed valve in the main gear wheel well.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Set Fuel Control Panel (P5) CROSSFEED switch to ON and visually confirm the valve drive moves from the closed (C) position to the open (O) position.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Set Fuel Control Panel (P5) CROSSFEED switch to OFF and visually confirm the valve drive moves from the open (O) position to closed (C) position.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Para>(Required by AD 2019-19-10) </Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Prior to each flight, verify crossfeed valve operates normally.  </Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Set Fuel Control Panel (P5) CROSSFEED switch to ON and after 15 seconds, confirm FUEL CROSSFEED advisory message does not display.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Set Fuel Control Panel (P5) CROSSFEED switch to OFF and after 15 seconds, confirm FUEL CROSSFEED advisory message does not display.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>For fuel balancing, do the FUEL BALANCE SYS Non-Normal Checklist.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
